````java
var x = new int[] {1, 2, 3, 4, 5};
var y = new int[] {5, 4, 3, 2, 1};
var b =    IntStream.range(0, x.length).allMatch(i -&gt; x[i] &lt;= y[i])
        &amp;&amp; IntStream.range(0, x.length).anyMatch(i -&gt; x[i] &lt;  y[i]);
````
